<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4890046>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 1. Dinichthys herzeri. A, AMNH 81 (holotype), incomplete nuchal plate in internal view. B, AMNH 73 (paratype), left inferognathal plate in lateral view. C, AMNH 34, left anterior superognathal in lateral view. D, AMNH 33, right posterior superognathal in lateral view. Reconstruction of six denticles in the posterior tooth row based on CMNH 7257. Drawings reproduced from Hlavin, 1976. Scale bars equal 3 cm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4890046/files/figure.png" .

